    "spell": {
        "name": "Vindicator's Mark",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You launch a magical dart at your hunted prey, which marks them with a nimbus only you can detect. Make a spell attack against the target. On a hit, you deal 2d4 spirit damage and the target is marked by a glowing nimbus of energy that only you can see. For the duration of your spell, the marked target takes an additional +2 damage from all your weapon or unarmed attacks. Invisible targets marked by your *vindicator's mark* are concealed to you, rather than undetected.  \n  \nYou can Dismiss the spell on your turn if your last action dealt damage to the target with a weapon or unarmed attack, instantly dealing an additional 2d6 spirit damage to it.",
        "subtype": "spell",
        "spell_type": "focus",
        "rank": 1,
        "traits": [
            {
                "name": "Uncommon",
